Runeforged (Covetous)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_COVETOUS	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Covetous	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against evocation spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against evokers and creatures with the fire subtype. Wielder gains fire resistance 5.	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
Runeforged (Miserly)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_MISERLY	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Miserly	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against illusion spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against illusionists and creatures from the Plane of Shadow. Dispels illusions when struck first 3/day as targeted dispel magic (CL13).	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
Runeforged (Jealous)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_JEALOUS	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Jealous	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against necromancy spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against necromancers and undead created by necromancy spells (not spawn or self-manifested). Absorbs three negative levels inflicted on the wielder per day.	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
Runeforged (Domineering)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_DOMINEERING	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Domineering	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against transmutation spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against transmuters and creatures with the shapechange subtype. Absorbs up to three harmful transmutation effects inflicted on the wielder per day.	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
Runeforged (Tyrannical)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_TYRANNICAL	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Tyrannical	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against conjuration spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against conjurers and summoned monsters. Casts dismissal (CL 13) at first three creatures with Extraplanar subtype struck, each day.	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
Runeforged (Sadistic)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_SADISTIC	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Sadistic	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against abjuration spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against abjurers and any creatures with an active abjuration spell effect. Shrouds wielder in a mock magic aura. When targeted with a dispelling effect, the effect targets mock aura instead, once every 24 hours. 	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
Runeforged (Parasitic)	KEY:RUNEFORGED_PARASITIC	NAMEOPT:TEXT=Parasitic	TYPE:Ammunition.Weapon	PLUS:2	VISIBLE:QUALIFY	SOURCEPAGE:p.57	PREMULT:1,[PRETYPE:1,Enhancement],[PRETYPE:1,Ammunition.Weapon]	SPROP:Wielder gets +2 morale bonus on saving throws against enchantment spells, takes -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks. Acts as a bane weapon (+2 to attack rolls and damage, +2d6 to damage) against enchanters and against creatures that are charmed, dominated, or under another creature's magic control. Automatically dispels enchantment effect on a struck creature with such an active effect (CL 13). On success, heals wielder 6d6. Excess hitpoints are gained as temporary hitpoints for 1 hour.	BONUS:SKILL|Diplomacy|-2
